About this item

  • 【Health Metrics Monitoring】These fitness watches for women and men pack 24/7 heart rate, blood oxygen, blood pressure monitors and sleep tracker. You could check those real-time health metrics anytime, anywhere conveniently on your wrist and check the all-day data record in the App.The sleep tracker keeps track of time spent in different sleep stages including REM, light sleep,deep sleep,and the time when you wake up, helps you to get a better understanding of your sleep quality.
  • 【115 sports modes & All-Day Activity Tracking】There are more than 115 sports modes tracking available in the activity trackers and smartwatches, covering almost all daily sports activities you can imagine, gives you new ways to train and advanced metrics for more information about your workout performance.The all-day activity tracking feature monitors your steps, distance, and calories burned all the day, so you can see how much progress you've made towards your fitness goals.
  • 【Notifications for Calls and Messages】Getting notifications for incoming calls and texts right away from your wrist while on the go, allowing you to stay connected with family and friends with calls, texts, and email, so you never miss an important call or message. You could see the caller's name, reject the call, mute the ring-tone, and read the whole text messages directly from the smart watch for android phones and iphone.
  • 【A Considerate Life Assistant】The fitness trackers for women and men provide you with more features including drinking water reminder, sedentary reminder,menstrual cycle reminder, real-time weather display, remote camera shooting, music control,timer,and do-not-disturb mode, making it a considerate life assistant.With the GPS connectivity, you could get a map of your workout route in the app for outdoor activity by connecting to your phone GPS.
  • 【1.47" HD-color Full Touch Screen】The curved-design 1.47" HD-color display and full touch screen ensures better visual and operating experience, everything is easier to see and operate, making this fitness tracker as intuitive to use as it is beautiful to look at.There are more than 150 watch face options for you to choose from in the App. You could also customize the smart watch face with photos from your own album. So it's easy to find the right look for the right moment.
  • 【Ultra Long Battery Life & IPX8 Waterproof】Simply charge the smart watches for men and women with a magnetic USB cable. It takes 1.5-2 hours to full charge the fitness watch. Each full charge supports 6-7 days heavy use or 10-12 days daily use. Its standby time is up to 30 days.This smart fitness watch is IP68 waterproof, which is safe for washing bands,taking a shower, workout in the rain and swimming.
  • 【Wide Compatibility】The smartwatches are compatible with Android 4.4 / iOS 8.4 or above smartphones . Its comfortable durable, replaceable and washable strap with secure clasp is adjustable between mix 5.0in and max 9.05in, offering comfortable fit for women and men.Its slim and stylish design makes the smart watch a perfect accessory for any outfit. Whether you're hitting the gym or heading to the office, this fitness watch will seamlessly blend into your daily routine.

Product Description

1.47'' Slim Smart Fitness Tracker Watch with 24/7 Heart Rate, Blood Oxygen, Blood Pressure, and Sleep Tracker for Women Men

Mindrose smart fitness watch is aimed to be a considerate fitness companion for you to take your fitness goals to the next level. Whether you're a fitness enthusiast, or just starting your journey to a healthier lifestyle, this fitness tracker has everything you need to track your progress and stay connected, stay informed, and stay motivated to achieve your fitness goals and lead a healthier, happier life.

As Beautiful as It is Intuitive to Use

Its slim and stylish design makes the smart watch a perfect accessory for any outfit. Whether you're hitting the gym or heading to the office, this fitness watch will seamlessly blend into your daily routine.

With a curved 1.47" HD color display and full touch screen functionality, the watch is as intuitive to use as it is beautiful to look at by providing you with a better visual and operating experience.

More Than 150 watch face options for you to choose from or just customize the watch face with photos from your own album. So it's easy to find the right look for the right moment.

5 brightness levels for display are available. You can adjust the brightness for display as you like to make colors appear consistent in different environments.

Simply Charge the fitness watch with a magnetic USB Cable(included the package). It takes 1.5-2 hours to full charge the fitness watch. Each full-charging supports 7 days heavy use or 10 days daily use. Its standby time is up to 30 days.

Powerful Sensors for Insights About Your Health Metrics

This activity tracker and smartwatch packs heart rate, blood pressure and blood oxygen monitor. You could check those real-time health metrics anytime, anywhere conveniently on your wrist and check the all-day data record in App. You could turn on 24/7 heart rate tracking in App to provide you complete information to help you manage your well-being, ensuring that you stay on top of your health and fitness goals.

100+ Sports Modes and All-Day Activity Tracking

There are more than 100 sports modes tracking available in the fitness tracker, covering almost all daily sports activities you can imagine, gives you new ways to train and advanced metrics for more information about your workout performance. With the GPS connectivity, you could get a map of your workout route and pace in the app during outdoor activity by connecting to your phone GPS.

The all-day activity tracking feature monitors your steps, distance, and calories burned all the day, so you can see how much progress you've made towards your fitness goals.

Better Sleep, Better Performance

The sleep tracker keeps track of time spent in differnt sleep stages including REM, light sleep,deep sleep,as well as when you might have woken up, helps you to get a better understandig of your sleep quality and ensurs that you get the rest you need to perform at your best.

You could set vibration alarms to wake you up gently without disterbing your beloved one.

Stay Connected, Stay Informed, Put Life Under Your Control

Call and Message Notification:

Get calls and texts notifications right away from your wrist while on the go, allow you to stay connected with family and friends with calls, texts, and email, so you never miss an important call or message. (Notification: You can see caller's name, reject call, mute the call ring, and read the whole message on the watch, but you can't anwer the call/message on the watch)

Sedentary Reminder: Keeping you moving throughout the day.

Drinking Water Reminder: Staying hydrated is essential for our overall health and well-being.

Menstrual Cycle Reminder: Your life is always under your control.

Real-time Weather Display: Be informed of real time weather at a glance.

Don't Disturb Mode: Set "don't disturb" mode for a certain period of time when you need to focus on something or simply want some uninterrupted time to relax.

IPX8 Waterproof: The fitness watch can withstand immersion in water for 30 minutes at a depth of up to 9.8 feet.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
5 out of 5 stars
Great fitness watch with a lot of functionality
I am very pleased with this fitness watch. It has all the functions I would really need.This watch uses Blutooth connectivity with the FitCloudPro app. The watch does come with a QR included in the user manual to scan and download this app. The set up is very simple and easy to do.I've used this watch for several days and am pretty pleased with the battery life. I went about 4 days and it had gone down about 50% which I didn't think was too bad. The charger connects to the magnetic dots on the back of the watch. The charger can either be connected to a USB block or plugged into a USB port on a computer or portable battery pack.The watch has a quick-release watch band so it is easy to change out the bands if you would like to make it more personal. The watch looks great on my wrist. It is lightweight, and the screen is just the right size for my small wrist.The watch face is very responsive. I can easily scroll through the different menus with ease. There are differnet menu options to change the look of the menu if you prefer. There are also many different watch faces you can change on your watch either directly through the watch or on the app you download.I really like the functions available on this watch such as tracking my blood pressure, heart rate, and oxygen levels. There is a function to allow you to make and receive phone calls straight on your watch which I find very convenient if I am away from my phone and a call comes through. Surprisingly, the little speaker is very clear and easy to hear from the other end. You can also add your phone contacts to your phone for easier access.You can also control your media such as playing music straight from your watch to your phone. When I tried it, it just picked right up where I left off what I was listening to. There is also a camera shutter option. I used this a couple of times. You have to turn on the phone camera and set it up where you want then shake your wrist with the watch. It has a 3 second countdown before taking the photo.Some other funtions that I like to use during exercise are the stop watch and timer. There is also an alarm clock funtion and a Find Phone option which is convenient as I seem to lose my phone quite often.The watch can receive notifications from emails, social media accounts, and text messages but you cannot repsond to them directly on the watch. When you get a notification, it appears on the top half of the screen and has to be tapped in order to read the message.The screen on the watch is very bright even on the lowest brightness setting. It is nice during the day as it is easy to see but in a darker area, the light is almost like having a flashlight on your wrist. The watch vibrates with all notifications unless you turn that off and, again, the vibration is pretty strong even on the lowest setting (it is very loud) but the vibration can be turned off. There is a battery saver function as well but I found out when you turn that on, the watch disconnected from the blutooth connection with my phone.There is also a lifetime warranty through the manufacturer but I have not set that up yet.I would certainly recommend this watch to anyone looking for a simple fitness watch with a lot of functionality.

    5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install, bright, clear watch!
    Reviewed in the United States on November 17, 2024
    Verified Purchase
    I have been getting to know my new H39 watch over the past few days. My first impression is that the display is really bright and sharp with good contrast and bigger numbers and letters than my last watch. That makes it easier for me to read.
    The software was easy to download and install on my phone and the screens in the software are clear and easy to understand. The watch was easy to pair (they refer to it as "bind") with the phone. A QR code appears on the watch that you scan with your phone to bind them.
    Unlike my last watch, all functions on this phone synchronized with my phone (I have an Android, a Samsung Galaxy S21 5G) right away and I also installed it on my partners phone... He has a Nord OnePlus. I'm getting accurate BP, blood ox and heart rate. I just swipe the watch face sideways and when I land on one of those functions they start testing right away without me having to hold down any buttons, etc to start the test. It is very slick!
    I've already made a phone call from the watch (through my phone, of course) and the dial screen has big numbers, the voice on the watch speaker was clear and the person I called could hear me clearly. I also easily had my watch tell my phone to take a photo.
    The find phone function works like a charm. The sound it activated on the lost phone is much easier to hear than the ring tone on that phone so it's easier to find it.
    There are many other functions like breathing training, exercise tracking, step counting, and controlling playing music through your phone.
    The most impressive thing is how easily the watch synchs to the phone and that all the functions worked immediately without having to go through a bunch of processes and false starts to get each one to work. On my last watch I never was able to get the bp, blood ox and heart rate functions working even though I contacted that company's service folks for help and had uninstalled and reinstalled the software, etc. None of that needed here!
    There are several watch face designs available to choose from right on the watch. All of them are bright and clear.
    All in all if you are looking for an easy to use, easy to see watch that is really handsome looking, this is the one to buy. The price is very reasonable and the customer service people respond immediately to any concern.
